data.description: CUSTOM BUILT STUNNING MID CENTURY RANCH...Situated on gorgeous (almost 3/4 acre lot) in coveted Cottonade Community.  Surrounded by mature loandscaping & lovely well cared for homes, you'll find this lovely oasis & neighborhood extraordinary in every way.  Looking for space, privacy and a solid well built home at a price that wont bust your housing budget,  Unique spacious & immaculate 3BR+ ranch with OVERSIZE 2 car garage may be just what you've been waiting for.  A combination of vintage & contemporary touches t/o. Lower level family room w/ wood burning fireplace has tons of space & storage for everyone & everything.  Includes basement w/workshop & garden shed. Impressive santuary inside & out & ultra private setting-an opportunity to live the life you deserve.  Tucked away from everything & everyone, yet ultra convenient location to Ft Bragg, major highways, shopping, schools, etc. Did I mention the amazing HW floors & views?  You have to see for yourself you wont be disappointed.
